Two (2) or three (3) of the mods require you to disable signature verification using Lucky Patcher; or they simply won't work.

One (1) or (2) of the games require your device to be rooted.

For installing the OBB move the extracted folder to SDCard/Android/OBB

This pack include over fifty-eight (58) modded android games.

More information on each on a per topic basis is available at www.DroidHax.com

Enjoy!
